{
    "AIF": {
        "nodes": [
            {
                "nodeID": "iss1",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "Does long covid count in law as a disability?"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_iss1",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "Whether or not long covid counts in law as a disability"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_iss1",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "pos1",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "Long covid is considered a disability in law if it has a substantial effect on day-to-day activities and lasts or is likely to last at least 12 months."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_pos1",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "In cases where long covid has a substantial effect on someone\u2019s ability to carry out day-to-day activities and where it lasts or seems likely to last at least 12 months, it will be considered a disability in law."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_pos1",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "arg1",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "The legal definition of a disability under section 6 of the Equality Act 2010 is an impairment with a substantial and long-term adverse effect on a person's ability to carry out normal day-to-day activities."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_arg1",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "the legal definition of a disability, given in section 6 of the Equality Act 2010, is an impairment that has a \u201csubstantial\u201d and \u201clong-term\u201d adverse effect on someone\u2019s \u201cability to carry out normal day-to-day activities\u201d."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_arg1",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "pos2",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "Employers should focus on the reasonable adjustments they can make rather than trying to determine if an employee's condition constitutes a disability."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_pos2",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "Employers should focus on the reasonable adjustments they can make rather than trying to work out if an employee's condition is a disability."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_pos2",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "iss2",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "What extra flexibility can be offered to workers with long covid?"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_iss2",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "what extra flexibility can be offered to workers with long covid"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_iss2",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "pos3",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "The Government is expanding the right to request flexible working through the Employment Relations (Flexible Working) Act 2023."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_pos3",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "plans to expand the right to request flexible working, some of which were being delivered by the Employment Relations (Flexible Working) Act 2023"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_pos3",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "iss3",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "What financial support is available to people unable to work due to long covid, particularly former key workers?"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_iss3",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "what financial support is available to people unable to work due to long covid, particularly former key workers"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_iss3",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "pos4",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "The Government does not plan to introduce additional special support specifically for key workers with long covid."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_pos4",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "the Government had no plans to introduce additional special support for key workers with long covid"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_pos4",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "arg2",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "Financial support via Universal Credit, New Style Employment and Support Allowance, and Personal Independence Payment is already available to those unable to work due to long covid regardless of their status as a key worker."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_arg2",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "The DWP already offers financial support through Universal Credit and New Style Employment and Support Allowance for people who are unable to work due to long-Covid, subject to them satisfying the eligibility criteria and contribution conditions. In addition, people with Long-Covid may be eligible for Personal Independence Payment. This support is available regardless of keyworker status."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_arg2",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "iss4",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "Should long covid be prescribed as an occupational disease for the purposes of Industrial Injuries Disablement Benefit?"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_iss4",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "Long covid is not currently prescribed as an occupational disease for the purposes of Industrial Injuries Disablement Benefit"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_iss4",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "pos5",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "The Industrial Injuries Advisory Council recommends that specific long covid complications be added to the list of prescribed diseases for IIDB entitlement."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_pos5",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "IIAC recommended the following be added to the list of prescribed diseases allowing entitlement to IIDB"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_pos5",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "arg3",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "The IIAC found convincing and consistent evidence that five serious pathological complications of long covid cause persistent impairment and loss of function in health and social workers."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_arg3",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "IIAC found \"convincing and consistent evidence\" of five serious pathological complications for health and social workers with long covid. These complications had been shown to cause persistent impairment and loss of function in some workers."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_arg3",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
